.\n\nOther cities with notable Muslim populations include:\n\n*   **Boston, Massachusetts**\n*   **Orlando, Florida**\n*   **Seattle, Washington**\n*   **Columbus, Ohio**\n*   **Nashville, Tennessee**\n\nIt's important to note that the Muslim population in the US is highly diverse, with people from various ethnic, cultural, and national backgrounds. Also, population numbers can change, so demographic information is always evolving.",
